From 812ee4602608792e8f8c6948ea503342936eec7b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Dev <dev@example.com>
Date: Tue, 7 Jul 2026 11:55:37 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] Part 3 [Spring]: REST API for supply/demand orders

- OrderController: POST /api/orders/supply and POST /api/orders/demand
- SupplyOrderRequest/DemandOrderRequest: bean-validated request DTOs
  (required fields, HH:mm time pattern, positive price/quantity)
- OrderService: bridges HTTP requests to the same MatchingEngine + JDBC
  persistence used by Parts 1 & 2; reloads open orders from DB on startup
- GlobalExceptionHandler: consistent JSON error responses for validation
  failures, bad input, and DB errors (e.g. duplicate order id -> 409)
- DemandSupplyApplication: Spring Boot entry point
