+
+## Part 3 [Spring] — REST API
+
+A Spring Boot web layer wraps the same `MatchingEngine` and JDBC persistence
+used in Parts 1 & 2. Every order submitted through the API is matched
+immediately and persisted, exactly like `Part2Main`.
+
+### Run it
+
+```bash
+mvn spring-boot:run
+```
+
+The app starts on **http://localhost:8080** (make sure MySQL is running and
+`db.properties` is configured, same as Part 2 — the API uses the same DB).
+
+### Endpoints
+
+| Method | Path                  | Body                                                                 |
+|--------|-----------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------|
